OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late sunny
OL,7,Fspells before turning cloudier from
OL,8,Fthe west. Becoming cloudy for all
OL,9,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fspreading eastwards.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy day with patchy
OL,13,Frain pushing eastwards and turning
OL,14,Fbriefly heavy at times in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Rain clearing to clear
OL,16,Fspells and scattered showers later in
OL,17,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
