OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with heavy showers Sunday.
OL,7,FDrier for a time Monday with sunny
OL,8,Fspells, then rain spreading east
OL,9,Flater. Strong winds at times Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith rain clearing to heavy showers.
